paragraphs.text:
%jdbc
SELECT "myapp_record"."item_id", "myapp_item"."name", CAST(SUM("myapp_item"."price") AS NUMERIC) AS "item__price__sum" 
FROM "myapp_record" INNER JOIN "myapp_item" ON ("myapp_record"."item_id" = "myapp_item"."id") 
GROUP BY "myapp_record"."item_id", "myapp_item"."name" 
ORDER BY "item__price__sum" DESC
LIMIT 10
